==Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|September|ja|9月|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft|12=draft}} of 甲戌. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Cold Dew|ja|寒露|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|立冬|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft}} for 甲戌 is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of 甲戌 is the 5th day of {{ill|Large Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=大土|12=draft|12=draft}}.


