{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Wood Dog|kanji=甲戌|romaji=kinoe inu|onyomi=kōjutsu|p=jiǎxū|w=chia-hsü|mi=ʈ͡ʂja̠²¹ ɕy⁵³|y=gaap6 seot1|j=gaap6 seot1|ci=kaːp̚ sœt̚|mc=kæp syt|oc-bs=kaːp ʔsuʔ}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}

'''Yang Wood Dog also known as 甲戌''' (kinoe inu, kouboku no inu, koujutsu) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 11th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Guiyou|ja|癸酉|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Otsugai|ja|乙亥|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|木|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Dog|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|12=draft|12=draft}}) (Wood overcomes Earth).  
==Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 14 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft}} of 甲戌.
