The day of 甲戌 is the 5th day of {{ill|Large Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=大土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=}}.

