bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}}) (Wood overcomes Earth). ==Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s Years== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 14 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of 甲戌. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 14|14 AD]] * [[:en:AD 74|74 AD]] * [[:en:AD 134|134 AD]] * [[:en:194|194 AD]] * [[:en:254|254 AD]] * [[:en:314|314 AD]] * [[:en:374|374 AD]] * [[:en:434|434 AD]] * [[:en:494|494 AD]] * [[:en:554|554 AD]] * [[:en:614|614 AD]] * [[:en:674|674 AD]] * [[:en:734|734 AD]] * [[:en:794|794 AD]] * [[:en:854|854 AD]] * [[:en:914|914 AD]] * [[:en:974|974 AD]] | * [[:en:1034|1034 AD]] * [[:en:1094|1094 AD]] * [[:en:1154|1154 AD]] * [[:en:1214|1214 AD]] * [[:en:1274|1274 AD]] * [[:en:1334|1334 AD]] * [[:en:1394|1394 AD]] * [[:en:1454|1454 AD]] * [[:en:1514|1514 AD]] * [[:en:1574|1574 AD]] * [[:en:1634|1634 AD]] * [[:en:1694|1694 AD]] * [[:en:1754|1754 AD]] * [[:en:1814|1814 AD]] * [[:en:1874|1874 AD]] * [[:en:1934|1934 AD]] * [[:en:1994|1994 AD]] | * {{ill|2054 AD|ja|2054年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2054|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2054 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2114 AD|ja|2114年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2114|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2114 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2174 AD|ja|2174年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2174|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2174 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2234 AD|ja|2234年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2234|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2234 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2294 AD|ja|2294年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2294|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2294 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2354 AD|ja|2354年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2354|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2354 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2414 AD|ja|2414年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2414|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2414 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2474 AD|ja|2474年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2474|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2474 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2534 AD|ja|2534年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2534|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2534 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2594 AD|ja|2594年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2594|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2594 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2654 AD|ja|2654年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2654|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2654 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2714 AD|ja|2714年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2714|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2714 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2774 AD|ja|2774年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2774|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2774 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2834 AD|ja|2834年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2834|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2834 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2894 AD|ja|2894年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2894|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2894 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2954 AD|ja|2954年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2954|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2954 AD|qq=}} |} ==Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s Months== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:September|September]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of 甲戌. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Hanlu|Cold Dew]] until the day before [[:en:Lidong|Beginning of Winter]]) as applicable. ==Yang Wood Dog (甲戌)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for 甲戌 is as follows. === Selected Day (選日) === The day of 甲戌 is the 5th day of {{ill|Large Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=大土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=}}.
