|2714 AD|ja|2714年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2714|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2714 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2774 AD|ja|2774年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2774|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2774 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2834 AD|ja|2834年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2834|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2834 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2894 AD|ja|2894年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2894|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2894 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2954 AD|ja|2954年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2954|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2954 AD|qq=}} |} ==Months of Yang Wood Dog== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:September|September]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of 甲戌. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Hanlu|Cold Dew]] until the day before [[:en:Lidong|Beginning of Winter]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Wood Dog== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for 甲戌 is as follows. === Selected Day (選日) === The day of 甲戌 is the 5th day of {{ill|Large Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=大土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=}}.
